      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "`deriveaddresses` doesn't create a new address, it just computes one based on a descriptor (this for example does not make the wallet automatically treat transactions to the generated address as incoming payments). For more information on descriptors, see https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/doc/descriptors.md.",
